run1.title: Morning exploring
run1.description: Woke up a little too late to get to practice so I did a quick run so that I can get to work on time and finish up my mileage later.

run2.description: Little evening run so that I can get mileage. I did a bunch of random running down little streets and exploring, similar to the morning run. I didn't feel the best but the run wasn't bad.
